# example input files to run CMD simulations
# in the NPT ensamble with i-PI + MACE

# input.xml: i-pi input file
# run-ase.py: python file to define the ASE-MACE calculator
# POSCAR and init.xyz: geometry input file (the xyz format file is specific to i-pi)

# the i-pi xyz format can be obtained with the script get_ipi_xyz_from_ase_xyz.py
# usage is
# python get_ipi_xyz_from_ase_xyz.py ase_format.xyz ipi_format.xyz
# where ase_format.xyz is the standard xyz format
